### Buscar Amostra por ID
# Substitua {id} pelo UUID da amostra
GET {{baseUrl}}/exames/amostras/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# {
#   "id": "uuid",
#   "codigoInterno": "SANG-EDTA-001",
#   "nome": "Sangue Total com EDTA",
#   "descricao": "...",
#   "tipoAmostra": "sangue",
#   "recipientePadrao": "Tubo com EDTA (tampa roxa)",
#   "volumeMinimo": 3,
#   "volumeIdeal": 5,
#   "requerJejum": true,
#   "tempoJejum": 8,
#   "temperaturaArmazenamento": "refrigerado",
#   "prazoValidadeHoras": 48,
#   "ativo": true,
#   ...
# }


